## Using `tbl_summary()`



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
library(gtsummary)
library(dplyr)

mtcars %>%
  select(vs) %>%  # select the vs variable
  tbl_summary(
    label = list(vs = "Engine Type"),  # change the label of the vs variable
    digits = vs ~ c(0, 1)  # set the number of digits, 0 for frequency and 1 for relative frequency
  )
```

